      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the requirements, the architecture, and the interfaces between the ICANN Trademark Clearinghouse (TMCH) and Domain Name Registries, as well as between the ICANN TMCH and Domain Name Registrars for the provisioning and management of domain names during Sunrise and Trademark Claims Periods.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
